---
title: Steak Sandwiches with Caramelized Onion and Roasted Tomato Salad
description: There's nothing like slices of juicy steak in a crusty ciabatta sandwich. Sweet caramelized red onions and roasted tomatoes really round out this take on a steakhouse dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steak-sandwiches-dfebcf20.jpg
